title: Halo Universal Binary
description:
Halo Universal Binary
Took me a while to find this so I though I would share it :)

- PowerPC and Intel Macs can now enjoy some Halo (naively)

- Use this serial when asked to put one in (ZAXG-FAJM-YEU5-UW29)
- Key above has worked for some and has failed for others
- The key does work with latest patch (2.0.3 I believe still)

- This can run on the Intel 950 GMA video card
- Works with MacFire (Xfire client for Mac, lookup Xblaze)
- This can run on Mac OS X 10.5.1 and 10.5.4 Leopard (Maybe 10.5.5 and 10.5.6)
- This has been tested on a Hackintosh
- Intel Graphic Card users will want to run game with Vertex Shaders only to have the best experience

Enjoy Another Great Torrent From Espionage724
